{"tid":553781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問健身奶粉食法(新手求解)","createTime":"2018-02-07T23:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T10:49:34.000Z","uid":159929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7101ad1f3c27f725b5e4d02bba69fda862065a54","tid":553781,"uid":159929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:10:17.000Z","msg":"我睇新聞奶粉唔可以一次過食咁多,正常D人講要分早餐後同運動後食. <br />\n<br />\n事因我要番工冇時間,所以要好早做GYM. 咁如果我早餐後食完即該去做GYM再運動後食,咁會唔會食太過量吸收唔到?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">專家教路：一次食太多蛋白質難吸收<br />\n<br />\n林思為更提醒﹕「別一次過食太多蛋白質，因為身體未必吸收到，最好分三餐食用。想增肌的健身人士建議每餐食30至40克，就算一餐食足90克，身體亦只吸收到40克左右。而且每餐最好有不同配搭，才達均衡營養。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170530/s00005/1496080482831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170530%2Fs00005%2F1496080482831&d=rbrA02%2FAu0L3nSa0hO7rOP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b2663d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170530%2Fs00005%2F1496080482831&h=6de5a59e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170530/s00005/1496080482831</a><br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c396abe23540584186007b045a6168d8fac3be95","tid":553781,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"realfood 嘅蛋白質係可以儲存喺身體分段吸收 , 係 whey 嘅蛋白質先係設計黎快速吸收"},{"pid":"78e1d83252f384abf427afc90480a91db1365e76","tid":553781,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用凍水定熱水沖<img src=\"/asse